</p><p class="- topic/p ">The machine will identify itself with this SOID to the back office systems. In ORS possibilities exist to override the sent SOID. Overrides should only be temporary. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Here is described how to change the SOID on the system.
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-B68CE9F8-6199-45B3-B424-95C9818D0853"><p class="- topic/p "> When changing the SOID, this will impact the visibility of this system in ORS. 
